          "id": "medmcqa-0fa8fbe2-b593-45d7-80be-84cbbe8d12c2",
          "text": "A married woman died in unnatural conditions within 5 years of her marriage. Her parents complained of frequent demand of dowry. Her autopsy will be conducted under which section: AI 10; Punjab 10",
