          "id": "medmcqa-eb3a4e60-5c9a-4589-b452-30137e64429f",
          "text": "A 6 hrs old snake bite patient come to emergency with mild local oedema at the injury site on examination no abnormality detected, laboratory investigation shows normal report, most appropriate management",
