          "text": "Differentiating feature of female pelvis is -a) Subpubic angle V shapedb) Subpubic angle U shaped and obtusec) Pre auricular sulcus is prominentd) Ischial tuberosity is everted and obturator foramen is large and ovale) Ischial tuberosity is everted and obturator foramen small and triangular",
