          "explanation": "Gagging It is caused when some pad or a piece of cloth is thrust into the mouth. It is usually resoed to prevent the victim from shouting for help, and death is usually not intended. Ref: TEXTBOOK OF FORENSIC MEDICINE AND TOXICOLOGY KRISHNAN VIJ FIFTH EDITION PAGE 116",
