          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "the synopsis of forensic medicine & toxicology; Dr k.s narayan reddy; 28th edition ;pg.no. 150 Multiple punctate lacerations of the face are produced due to the shattering of the wind screen glass into multiple small fragments with relatively blunt edges (SPARROW FOOT MARKS) .",
