          "id": "medmcqa-3d366dc9-c1ef-45d8-b882-f6577001e942",
          "text": "You are a forensic surgeon examining the hair sample obtained from a crime scene. The following are the findings: Hair diameter is 120 micrometer; cross section is rounded ; pigmentation is dense auburn through the cross section; cuticle is thick; undulations are rare. What race does the hair most probably belong to?",
