          "explanation": "The cross section of the hair is kidney shape in Negroid, oval in Caucasoid and round in Mongoloid. The cuticle is thick in case of Mongoloid. It is not so in Caucasoid. Fuhermore the pigmentation pattern is also suggestive of Mongoloid race. Ref: Textbook of Forensic Medicine and Toxicology by V.V Pillay, 15th Edition, Page 56."
