          "id": "medmcqa-99a99979-7e13-4b37-9067-f42d1a15c0e3",
          "text": "Heera lals's 10 year old child presented in casualty with snake bite since six hours. On examination no systemic signs are found and lab investigations are normal except localized leg swelling <5 cm. Next step in management.",
