          "explanation": "the given image is papaver somniferum / opium poppy. The only body secretion that is not impaired in opium poisoning is sweat. All other secretions are decreased. Skin in opium poisoning is moist and cold (impoant to distinguish it from other poisonings) patient manifest with low Blood pressure, Slow pulse, slow respiration.",
